sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as REST Client
    participant Proxy as rest-proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant Marshaler as Custom Marshaler<br/>(JSON ↔ Tensor)
    participant Gateway as gRPC-Gateway<br/>(generated code)
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh gRPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (POST /v2/models/{name}/infer)
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Optional TLS
        Proxy->>Marshaler: Parse JSON request body<br/>Flatten multi-dim arrays<br/>Decode base64 BYTES tensors
        Marshaler->>Gateway: InferRequest protobuf message
        Gateway->>ModelMesh: gRPC ModelInfer RPC<br/>Optional TLS (localhost:8033)
        ModelMesh-->>Gateway: InferResponse protobuf
        Gateway-->>Marshaler: Marshal response
        Marshaler-->>Proxy: JSON with tensor data<br/>Encode raw bytes / base64
        Proxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>Optional TLS
    end

    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request (GET /v2/models/{name})
        Client->>Proxy: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>Optional TLS
        Proxy->>Gateway: Route to ModelMetadata RPC
        Gateway->>ModelMesh: gRPC ModelMetadata RPC<br/>Optional TLS (localhost:8033)
        ModelMesh-->>Gateway: ModelMetadataResponse protobuf
        Gateway-->>Proxy: Marshal to JSON
        Proxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>Model metadata
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 3: Versioned Inference (POST /v2/models/{name}/versions/{ver}/infer)
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/versions/{ver}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json
        Proxy->>Marshaler: Parse JSON, extract version
        Marshaler->>Gateway: InferRequest with model_version
        Gateway->>ModelMesh: gRPC ModelInfer RPC<br/>(with version)
        ModelMesh-->>Gateway: InferResponse protobuf
        Gateway-->>Marshaler: Marshal response
        Marshaler-->>Proxy: JSON with tensor data
        Proxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response
    end
